Arvato Supply Chain Solutions is part of Bertelsmann. We combine the advantages of a global corporation with the reliability of a family-run business. We take care of our 15.000 employees in more than 20 countries who profit from a wide range of benefits and professional development programs.
(Junior) SAP Consultant – Heijen – Arvato SCS
Is SAP is your thing? Do you want to get involved, implement your own ideas in the SAP world of logistics, be responsible for your own actions and learn something new every day? Are you looking for a company that recognizes and promotes your talents, supports your professional ambitions and gives you responsibility at an early stage? We, Arvato Supply Chain Solutions, offer you exactly this perspective. As a (Junior) SAP Consultant at our location in Heijen or Germany (Gütersloh, Hamburg) you will be part of innovative, exciting and varied projects. Develop yourself professionally and personally with a steep learning curve and become a proven SAP expert with consulting skills.

We offer
Are you ambitious and looking for a challenge? Then our dynamic working environment characterized by team orientation, personal responsibility and creative freedom is the perfect match for you!
Continuous learning is embedded in our DNA and culture. We promote your network and your further development with a wide range of network events, e-learning and individual training tailored to your needs and knowledge;
We work in flat hierarchies, which are reflected in our informal culture and quick decision-making processes. Be yourself - even with the dress code and work with modern technical equipment in a cloud-based IT environment;
Work the way that suits you best. We offer you flexible working time models with mobile office shares;

Your tasks
You will learn and support the conception, implementation and further development of exciting introductory and support projects for our international customers and you will increasingly develop into responsible tasks;
As a team player, you get involved in the conception and implementation of new processes;
You get an insight into the customizing of settings in SAP SD/MM, TM and/or (E)WM and later adopt them independently;
You are responsible for sub-project tasks for new customer implementations;
You will learn how system and process documentation is carried out and later identify optimization potential for our customers within the scope of process analyses.

Your profile
Successfully completed studies in computer science, business informatics, engineering or a comparable course of study or equivalent training and further education, e.g. as an IT specialist with initial professional experience;
First points of contact in the SAP environment, ideally in the context of internships, working student activities or smaller projects, as well as initial experience in dealing with agile methods;
Basic knowledge of programming (e.g. ABAP);
Great enthusiasm for innovative SAP topics and digitization topics;
Good understanding of the English language.


Working at arvato Benelux B.V. means working as part of a fast-growing international provider of marketing, communications and logistics services with offices in Abcoude, Maastricht, Schiphol-Rijk, Venlo,Venray and new location Gennep.
For more information look at our website: www.werkenbijarvato.nl.

We are looking forward to receive your application
For questions regarding this vacancy please contact Annabelle Gorissen via recruitment@arvato-scs.com

